### Generate OTP

The endpoint triggers an HTTP POST request to generate a one-time password (OTP) for the provided email address.

#### **Access Control:**

- **Role Required:** No Role Required


#### Request Body

- email (string): The email address for which the OTP needs to be generated.


#### Response Body

The response will be in JSON format with the following schema:

``` json
{
  "id": {
    "type": "integer"
  },
  "email": {
    "type": "string"
  },
  "otp": {
    "type": "string"
  },
  "createdDateTime": {
    "type": "string",
    "format": "date-time"
  }
}

 ```

